<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<title>Document</title>
	<style>
	*{
		margin: 0;
		padding: 0;
	}
		#wrap{
			width: 1200px;
			height: 600px;
			margin: 0 auto;
			margin-top: 50px;
			border: 5px solid red;
			padding: 30px;
			overflow: hidden;
		}
		#child{
			width: 600px;
			height: 500px;
			border: 4px solid green;
			float: left;
			overflow:auto;

		}
		#child1{
			width: 800px;
			height: 700px;
			background-color:pink;
		}
		#right{
			float: left;
			margin-left: 50px;
		}
		input{
			width: 400px;
			height: 50px;
			border: 1px solid gray;
			background-color: rgb(200,200,200);
			color: black;
			text-align: center;
			border-radius: 12px;
			margin: 0 auto;
		}
	</style>
</head>
<body>
	<div id="wrap">
		<div id="parent">
			<div id="child">
				<div id="child1">
					<p>床前明月光，疑是地上霜，举头望明月，低头思故乡。</p>
					<p>噫吁嚱，危乎高哉！蜀道之难，难于上青天！ 蚕丛及鱼凫，开国何茫然！
                      尔来四万八千岁，不与秦塞通人烟。西当太白有鸟道，可以横绝峨眉巅。 
                      地崩山摧壮士死，然后天梯石栈相钩连。上有六龙回日之高标，下有冲波逆折之回川。
                      黄鹤之飞尚不得过，猿猱欲度愁攀援。青泥何盘盘，百步九折萦岩峦</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div id="right">
				<ul>
					<li>scrollWidth : <span id="li1"></span></li>
                    <li>scrollHeight : <span id="li2"></span></li>
                    <li>scrollTop : <span id="li3"></span></li>
                    <li>scrollLeft : <span id="li4"></span></li>
                    <br>
                    <hr width="500px">
                    <br>
                    <li>offsetParent : <span id="li9"></span></li>
                    <li>offsetWidth : <span id="li5"></span></li>
                    <li>offsetHeight : <span id="li6"></span></li>
                    <li>offsetTop : <span id="li7"></span></li>
                    <li>offsetLeft : <span id="li8"></span></li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	<script type="text/javascript">
    function req(){
          var div = document.getElementById("child");
          document.getElementById("li1").innerHTML = (div.scrollWidth)+"px";//div1距离屏幕顶部的距离
          document.getElementById("li2").innerHTML = (div.scrollHeight)+"px";//div1距离屏幕左部的距离
          document.getElementById("li3").innerHTML = (div.scrollTop)+"px";//div1纵向滚动条滚动的距离
          document.getElementById("li4").innerHTML = (div.scrollLeft)+"px";//div1横向滚动条滚动的距离
          document.getElementById("li9").innerHTML = (div.offsetParent.tagName);
          document.getElementById("li5").innerHTML = (div.offsetWidth)+"px";
          document.getElementById("li6").innerHTML = (div.offsetHeight)+"px";
          document.getElementById("li7").innerHTML = (div.offsetTop)+"px";
          document.getElementById("li8").innerHTML = (div.offsetLeft)+"px";
     }
</script>
	<input type="botton" value="点击" onclick="req()">
</body>
</html>